question: Taun sabaraha paningkatan absolut pangbadagna dina 'Net interest income excluding cib markets' tina taun saméméhna?
Sabaraha rata-rata 'aset anu ngahasilkeun bunga rata-rata' dina tilu taun anu disayogikeun?
Dina taun iraha 'cib markets net interest income' pangluhurna, sabaraha niléy 'average cib markets interest-earning assets' nalika éta?
Kumaha tren 'net interest yield on average cib markets interest-earning assets' ti taun 2015 nepi ka 2017?
answer: Trensina kacida dinamis. Pamulang hasil naék kira-kira 17,3% tina 1,04 di 2015 nepi ka 1,22 di 2016, tapi lajeng ngalaman turunna seukeut kira-kira 29,5%, turun ka 0,86 di 2017.

question: Sebutkeun taun-taun iraha 'cib markets net interest income' leuwih ti $5.000 juta jeung 'net interest yield on average cib markets interest-earning assets' leuwih ti 1.10.
Dina taun 2016, sabaraha persén tina 'rata-rata aset anu ngahasilkeun bunga' sakabéhna anu diwangun ku 'aset pasar cib anu ngahasilkeun bunga'?
Upami 'cib markets net interest income' dina taun 2017 naek 20% sedengkeun 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' tetep sarua, sabaraha 'net interest income excluding cib markets' anu anyar?

Numutkeun kana tabel, naha aya korelasi anu kaciri antara 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' total sareng 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' dina tilu taun?
answer: Leres, aya korelasi positif anu jelas. Nalika 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' teras-terasan ningkat tina $44.620 juta dina 2015 dugi ka $51.410 juta dina 2017, 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' ogé nunjukkeun paningkatan anu konsisten tina 2,14% dugi ka 2,36% dina periode anu sami.

question: Taun sabaraha data 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' mangrupa outlier tina segi tumuwuhna ti taun ka taun dibandingkeun jeung periode séjén?
answer: Taun 2017 mangrupa outlier alatan tumuwuhna leuwih luhur sacara signifikan. Paningkatan ti taun 2016 ka 2017 nyaéta $4.118 juta ($51.410 - $47.292), anu leuwih gedé pisan dibandingkeun paningkatan $2.672 juta anu katempo ti taun 2015 nepi ka 2016 ($47.292 - $44.620).
